{
  "stem": "16503.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I mean, that shooting and-- and disposing of people's life-- lives-- in front of your eyes is something to see at the age of not quite-- no, I was 14 by then.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And there was a group of women who were in a much better physical shape than we were.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And they took my mother into their confidence and told her that, now that there is such a tremendous panic and-- and disorganization, that this is the only chance to cover yourself up in the hay in the morning and let the march continue and stay behind so that you-- that the front is right behind.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there were two possibilities, and my mother was a very cautious person.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was not-- she-- she felt that, number one, they will shoot into the hay.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Number two, she said she will-- they will take the big forks and go through the hay.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Number three, she said it's the Russians who are coming, and what are the Russians going to know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They won't know if it is-- if we are-- if the Germans or no-- or not.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if we are not in a proper group and not identified, they will shoot us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she was really petrified to make the decision to stay.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we did not stay.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The women did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a group of women which stayed, which I will come later to.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they did, but we continued.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we continued this march, and we finished in Gross Rosen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That I cannot tell you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Approximately, it must have been end of January, maybe beginning of February, but I am not really sure because Gross Rosen was just a pit stop because there was a complete hysteria of the Germans, believe it or not, of disposing of us.",
      "word_count": 43
    }
  ],
